'''Apprentice Felix''' is a wizard apprenticed to [[Wizard Traiborn]], he can be found on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} of the [[Wizards' Tower]]. After the player has completed the quest [[Temple of the Eye]], he can be found in the [[Temple of the Eye (location)|Temple of the Eye]]. Players can purchase unique [[Runecraft]] gear from [[Temple Supplies|his shop]] in exchange for [[abyssal pearls]] earned from the [[Guardians of the Rift]] [[Minigames|minigame]].

